Araxytes, known simply as "spider" in-game, are venomous spiders found in the Morytania Spider Nest. As they are abundant in numbers, able to inflict venom, and in a multicombat area, it is dangerous to fight them without prayer or a method to stave off venom.

During A Night at the Theatre, four of them attack the player upon obtaining some strange spider eggs.
